<FIRST>u i BC-Japan-Stocks     11-21 0026</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Japan-Stocks,0025</SECOND>
<HEAD>Stocks Up In Tokyo</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Nikkei Stock Average closed at 36,059.87, up
166.29 points, on the Tokyo Stock Exchange Tuesday.
</TEXT>
</DOC>
