fair; Chattanooga 58 fair; Cincinnati 37 fair; Cleveland 32 windy;
Detroit 29 windy; Hatteras 60 fair; Jacksonville 51 fair; Key West
70 fair; Knoxville 46 fair; Macon 55 fair; Miami 62 fair; New York
41 windy; Philadelphia 41 windy; Pittsburgh 30 partly cloudy;
Portland, Maine, 39 rain; Richmond 54 windy; Tampa 56 fair;
Washington, D.C., 45 windy.
   _CENTRAL: Bismarck 32 partly cloudy; Chicago 32 fair; Denver 30
fair; Des Moines 31 fair; Indianapolis 33 fair; Kansas City 35
fair; Little Rock 56 fair; Louisville 44 fair; Memphis 56 fair;
Nashville 49 fair; New Orleans 65 foggy; North Platte 23 fair;
Oklahoma City 52 partly cloudy; Omaha 31 fair; Rapid City 27 fair;
St. Louis 40 fair; Minneapolis-St. Paul 27 cloudy; Sault St. Marie
16 fair; San Antonio 62 foggy.
