of it,'' said Podsadowski's wife, Lisa.
   The Podsadowskis treated the Dalleys to dinner Friday at a
restaurant, where Francestown residents gathered and gave the
Dalleys the gift.
   ``It's hard to express how moving it was,'' Mrs. Dalley said.
``The next day, I cried all day.''
   The robber remains at large.
