risen 0.19 to 188.22.
   At the American Stock Exchange, the market value index was up
0.23 at 371.71.
   On Monday, the Dow Jones industrial average dropped 20.62 points
to 2,632.04.
   Declining issues outnumbered advances by more than 2 to 1 on the
NYSE, with 467 up, 1,008 down and 484 unchanged.
   Big Board volume totaled 128.17 million shares, down from 151.02
million in last Friday's session.
